name: Deus Ex Mens
text: Defender, reach, deathtouch False Faith: Green - When Deus Ex Mens enter the battlefield, if you control a green enchantment, look at the top eight cards of your library. You may reveal two enchantment cards and/or land cards from among them and put them into your hand. Then shuffle. Whenever an enchantment enters the battlefield under your control, you gain 1 life and draw a card.
